        "summary": "Enable TagFocus",
        "description": "Instructs already-inventoried tags to remain unresponsive, improving the reader's ability to find difficult-to-read tags. Targets tags in session S1.\n\n**Topic:** `controlrequest`\n\n**Response Topic:** `controlresponse`",
        "operationId": "enableTagFocus",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
